<section class="container my-5">
  <h2 class="text-center">Focus Roles &amp; Areas of Development</h2>
  <p class="text-center">At the HIVE, we target four ares of development. We tailor our modify our approach depending on the age category.</p>

  <!-- =========================
       Desktop: Column-colored table
       ========================= -->
  <div class="d-none d-lg-block">
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table class="table hive-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th scope="col"></th>
